# ThreatLoom - Cyber Threat Intelligence Fusion Hub

A comprehensive threat intelligence dashboard for Splunk Cloud/Enterprise.

## Features

-   Real-time threat monitoring
-   Interactive dashboards
-   Threat analytics and correlation
-   Incident response workflows

## Installation

1. Upload the ThreatLoom app to your Splunk environment
2. Restart Splunk
3. Navigate to the ThreatLoom app

## Building from Source

Run `node build.js` to build the React app and prepare for Splunk deployment.

## Version

1.0.0
